   @{b}*@{ub} Open Library Window

     opens a window showing the libraries.  If you doubleclick on a
     library entry it opens a @{b}FD:@{ub} window that shows all functions of
     the library when the library is defined in the @{b}Barfly.FD@{ub} file.
