Address Optimizing
------------------

   @{b}*@{ub}     @{b}Long@{ub}

     +---------------+----------------+---------------------+--------+
     | Addressmode   |   Optimizing   |         Note        | Option |
     +---------------+----------------+---------------------+--------+
     +---------------+----------------+---------------------+--------+
     |     x.l,EA    |    x.w,EA      | $ffff8000<=x<=$7fff |        |
     +---------------+----------------+---------------------+  -OAL  |
     |     EA,x.l    |    EA,x.l      | $ffff8000<=x<=$7fff |        |
     +---------------+----------------+---------------------+--------+

   @{b}*@{ub}     @{b}x(an)@{ub}

     +---------------+----------------+---------------------+--------+
     | Addressmode   |   Optimizing   |         Note        | Option |
     +---------------+----------------+---------------------+--------+
     +---------------+----------------+---------------------+--------+
     |   x(an),EA    |    (an),EA     |         x=0         |        |
     +---------------+----------------+---------------------+  -OAX  |
     |   EA,x(an)    |    EA,(an)     |         x=0         |        |
     +---------------+----------------+---------------------+--------+

   @{b}*@{ub}     @{b}PC-Relative@{ub}

     +---------------+----------------+---------------------+--------+
     | Addressmode   |   Optimizing   |         Note        | Option |
     +---------------+----------------+---------------------+--------+
     +---------------+----------------+---------------------+--------+
     |   label,EA    |  label(pc),EA  | $ffff8000<=x<=$7fff |  -OAP  |
     +---------------+----------------+---------------------+--------+

   @{b}*@{ub}     @{b}A4-Smalldata@{ub}

     +---------------+----------------+---------------------+--------+
     | Addressmode   |   Optimizing   |         Note        | Option |
     +---------------+----------------+---------------------+--------+
     +---------------+----------------+---------------------+--------+
